# MindOpt warm-start parameters — loaded by the gtopt MindOpt backend (via
# MDOreadparams) as a sibling of the case's main mindopt.prm when
# SolverOptions::advanced_basis is active.  Mirrors cplex_warmstart.prm.
#   Method 0   primal simplex — warm off the resident basis (1 = dual).
#   Presolve 0 keep the resident advanced basis valid.
Method 0
Presolve 0
